Package: lagerspetz-meta-games
Maintainer: Eemil Lagerspetz <eemil@gmx.com>
Architecture: all
Version: 1.0.0
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: dosbox, fluid-soundfont-gm, joystick, lutris, playonlinux, pavucontrol, paprefs, steam-launcher, timidity, xboxdrv, zero-k
Recommends: bumblebee-nvidia, nouveau-firmware, nvidia-settings, primus
Suggests:
Description: metapackage pulling in steam, lutris, etc gaming platforms.
 This package is meant to shorten the list of manually installed packages on Ubuntu/Mint systems, and to help replicate a configuration on a new machine.
